  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-71658ccc-00b7-43b9-a13b-3f8bf84225f8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-b10b538a-5213-429d-ab2f-5d7c156c6cbf\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-74a9e43e-7433-4e81-b725-ca785da1ac3d\"><b>몸과 마음을 건강하게!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-4ef02158-a2a8-4ea9-b238-d139489eeac7\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-f73b1dc8-4abd-4ceb-8b7a-b3a0b661ff7d\"><b>안녕하세요, </b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#fff8b2;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-16e30c7d-41bf-4de7-99eb-81f813dcfc09\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-da1e9f6b-faa9-40d1-b9f6-ffc07bb02612\"><b>입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-71658ccc-00b7-43b9-a13b-3f8bf84225f8\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f14e7c6-1b55-401d-9b45-0b1563a9a99c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"2\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_2.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-30fcb7b1-1e88-4836-901a-8d6ce9dc1a13\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-69ed4e8c-61b9-4899-a2e9-5d7f20c594e0\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5436532e-1156-4737-b347-501654ae6f61\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-3cc12670-98bc-443e-9760-70da9d9aa30f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b21680ef-69d8-4df1-8cdb-4869ef77399a\"><b>요즘 현대인들은 일상 속 스트레스와 긴장 속에서 살아가는데요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-23efcb7f-4442-4bdb-9b77-f7d4e5420d75\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e6de8872-8cc0-4afa-8d13-18b165101202\"><b> 많은 분들이 찾는 한방 처방 중 하나가 ‘우황청심원’입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d596bfc7-e5ee-4fb6-89a3-5508547b0657\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9b2d949e-5df4-4eb0-9f18-3177e8925aa1\"><b>그렇다면, 우황청심원은 어떤 약일까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-30fcb7b1-1e88-4836-901a-8d6ce9dc1a13\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-cf07b99d-c7fe-4b54-a35e-5d86ca9c940f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc7ac7d4-c4bc-4683-b0b0-9b8e8bdb32b5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-bc7ac7d4-c4bc-4683-b0b0-9b8e8bdb32b5\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/abf1b251a627b826.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1500\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1500\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/abf1b251a627b826.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/abf1b251a627b826.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-bc7ac7d4-c4bc-4683-b0b0-9b8e8bdb32b5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-e93c21aa-28d3-4585-b710-19c3e93922cf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-57617c6d-f4ee-4617-b3a3-f4d4892cfa0f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e24b99f8-6e20-4a1c-848f-37026204305b\"><b>우황청심원이란?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a1ef173-b178-460d-b989-da802901bbe6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-34f4c99d-7090-48f7-a6f9-c748b7753231\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a17da0b0-f8fa-45c3-ac40-adc15f3849c6\">우황청심원(牛黃淸心元)은 조선시대 왕실에서도 애용되었던 대표적인 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-56d5d7c1-f962-480a-9c48-169b776bd6d9\"><b>한방 구급약</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5094ea2a-b7c1-4060-b755-f04ceb6afedb\">입니다. ‘우황(牛黃)’이라는 성분이 핵심이며, 열을 내려주고 진정시켜주는 효능이 있는 다양한 한약재가 복합적으로 들어 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-51693de1-db7c-45bf-9a66-92176affaeb2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c375c140-2ec8-47ec-8807-a3670fdd46e0\">예로부터 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-76fec430-4e95-4e95-9b33-64920e0a234f\"><b>심신이 극도로 긴장하거나 열이 갑자기 오를 때</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-23ae2c56-32b9-4bb7-82a5-0979c8ecdcf6\">, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-42e53c57-33d1-4ef7-bf5a-b8b024061964\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e5d4c0c3-be64-4aaa-8fe6-a81907b3655a\">정신을 안정시키기 위해 복용해 왔습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-4a1ef173-b178-460d-b989-da802901bbe6\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-66b9b7e0-108a-4b19-9e29-f15cce2a2356\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-66b9b7e0-108a-4b19-9e29-f15cce2a2356\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a055ec960d0e9aab.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1536\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a055ec960d0e9aab.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a055ec960d0e9aab.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"332\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-66b9b7e0-108a-4b19-9e29-f15cce2a2356\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-386cd432-f7fb-43ce-924f-4d72d0d410d1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-0f08fe47-5ed0-4c41-8b00-a218c5727300\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-69a16069-7233-45eb-bd32-09bbc14d9937\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7ecec21a-6ade-4c06-a757-9ba0a5c56671\"><b>어떨때 도움이 될까?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6bd62797-f1fd-460b-a7e1-374d28aaa2bb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b4a805e4-9931-4c02-8cd1-d15e5c6c74b9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-57f87000-9e78-4276-9972-92164e44333b\">시험, 면접 등으로 극도로 긴장되고 심장이 두근거릴 때</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-736e19df-b0a2-4072-894d-6af4c7cb3d36\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c72e4e19-5fe0-458f-b4f3-85e63d38195e\">가슴이 답답하고 불안감이 갑자기 밀려올 때</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-24a0b559-57bd-4b90-b114-6a039286bff8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-70d2b045-374b-48cf-9437-06407d7e792c\">격한 감정이나 스트레스로 인해 평소보다 쉽게 흥분하거나 초조할 때</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-38124207-f9ab-41dc-a450-2455a95c9bda\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a7f7239c-410e-4e61-a417-02b057b6b7d1\">노약자에게 일시적으로 어지러움이나 의식이 흐려질 때</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1907520b-62dd-49f0-9e58-0ccbde2449c6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-161bf465-34b8-4eae-b0cc-44d54a8b28b4\">단, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1aaf738b-dde9-4490-9945-29c5d63cc2b6\"><b>심각한 의식 저하나 응급 상황</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f1c7ba86-e134-40ec-a447-a82fd7ea8364\">에서는 반드시 병원 진료를 먼저 받아야 하며, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-69705730-c4a9-47bb-841a-a72e274ecb43\"><b>우황청심원은 어디까지나 보조적인 구급용</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8fcad098-f96d-4611-a11e-db4e1e68261b\">으로 사용되는 점을 잊지 말아야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6bd62797-f1fd-460b-a7e1-374d28aaa2bb\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-c69bfed8-ac67-4648-a4f9-5406125ecee9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-234b4c47-621f-4e2e-93be-e64e9c06b372\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-447d093c-ea65-45af-9397-0be0b49d3cfd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-73964cfe-37fe-4a6f-91da-49f65de5ca64\"><b>주의사항</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-933f9051-956a-4103-8bee-5a7ac6f3cd43\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84dc1f96-f683-41cb-b52a-809b719a6926\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d1db7317-6eb6-4417-a7f3-1b269751a931\">우황청심원은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c8a0830f-5a92-4cda-9f2f-3d0c70620fd6\"><b>갑작스러운 증상이 발생했을 때 한 번 복용</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7376cbbc-ba79-4aab-9f5a-f1f2cd977ef3\">하는 방식으로 사용되며, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a4366798-6adc-4268-b97f-4258e88fdb3e\"><b>상시 복용하는 약은 아닙니다</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6c4938df-5d74-4a85-9dc6-b98bbb9b5407\">.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-51720da9-15a5-497e-9d9b-37cc42ff4ef2\"><span style=\"\" 